&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>अच्युतं केशवं रामनारायणं कृष्णदामोदरं वासुदेवं हरिम्। &lt;br>
श्रीधरं माधवं गोपिकावल्लभं जानकीनायकं रामचंद्रं भजे॥1॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Vishnu SahasraNaam - श्रीविष्णुसहस्रनामस्तोत्रम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/vishnu-sahasranaam/</link><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/vishnu-sahasranaam/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Vishnu.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">श्रीविष्णुसहस्रनामस्तोत्रम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%B6%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Vishnu SahasraNaam
&lt;div id="vishnu-sahasranaam" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#vishnu-sahasranaam" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>There are 5 versions of VishnuSahasraNaamStotram. They differ in their Dhyana Stotram, FalaStuti, or in the Main body of verses.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>विष्णुसहस्रनामस्तोत्रम् (महाभारतान्तर्गतम्)&lt;/strong>  (Mentioned Below) It has following types of verses
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Introductory Verses&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Verses for Purva Nyasa&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Dhyana Verses&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Main Verses&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Verses for Purva Nyasa&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Additional Concluding Verses&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Alternative Concluding Verses&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://sanskritdocuments.org/doc_vishhnu/viShNusahasranAmastotragaruDapurANa.html?lang=sa" target="_blank">विष्णुसहस्रनामस्तोत्रम् (गरुडपुराणान्तर्गतम्)&lt;/a> &lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://sanskritdocuments.org/doc_vishhnu/viShNusahasranAmastotranAradapancharAtra.html?lang=sa" target="_blank">विष्णुसहस्रनामस्तोत्रम् (नारदपञ्चरात्रान्तर्गतम्)&lt;/a> &lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://sanskritdocuments.org/doc_vishhnu/viShNusahasranAmastotrapadmapurana.html?lang=sa" target="_blank">विष्णुसहस्रनामस्तोत्रम् वासुदेवसहस्रनामस्तोत्रम् च (पद्मपुराणान्तर्गतम्) |&lt;/a> &lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://sanskritdocuments.org/doc_vishhnu/viShNusahasranAmastotramskandapurANa.html?lang=sa" target="_blank">विष्णुसहस्रनामस्तोत्रम् (स्कन्दपुराणान्तर्गतम्)&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h3 class="relative group">&lt;strong>Introductory Verses&lt;/strong>
&lt;div id="introductory-verses" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#introductory-verses" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>नारायणं नमस्कृत्य नरं चैव नरोत्तमम् । &lt;br>
देवीं सरस्वतीं व्यासं ततो जयमुदीरयेत् ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Mangalacharan - मङ्गलाचरणम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/mangalacharan/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/mangalacharan/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Vishnu.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">मङ्गलाचरणम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%99%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%99%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Mangalacharan
&lt;div id="mangalacharan" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#mangalacharan" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>॥ ॐ श्री गुरुभ्यो नमः हरिः ॐ ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>शुक्लाम्बरधरं विष्णुं शशिवर्णं चतुर्भुजम् । &lt;br>
प्रसन्नवदनं ध्यायेत् सर्वविघ्नोपशान्तये ॥ १॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>अगजानन पद्मार्कं गजाननमहर्निशम् । &lt;br>
अनेकदं तं भक्तानां एकदन्तमुपास्महे ॥ २॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>वागर्थाविव सम्पृक्तौ वागर्थप्रतिपत्तये । &lt;br>
जगतः पितरौ वन्दे पार्वतीपरमेश्वरौ ॥ ३॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>गुरुर्ब्रह्मा गुरुर्विष्णुः गुरुर्देवो महेश्वरः । &lt;br>
गुरुस्साक्षात् परब्रह्म तस्मै श्री गुरवे नमः ॥ ४॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>VishnuSuktam - विष्णुसूक्तम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/vishnusuktam/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/vishnusuktam/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Vishnu.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">विष्णुसूक्तम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">VishnuSuktam
&lt;div id="vishnusuktam" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#vishnusuktam" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>ॐ विष्णो॒र्नुकं॑ वी॒र्या॑णि॒ प्रवो॑चं॒ यः पार्थि॑वानि विम॒मे रजाग्ं॑सि॒ &lt;br>
यो अस्क॑भाय॒दुत्त॑रग्ं स॒धस्थं॑ विचक्रमा॒णस्त्रे॒धोरु॑गा॒यो &lt;br>
विष्णो॑र॒राट॑मसि॒ विष्णोः᳚ पृ॒ष्ठम॑सि॒ विष्णोः॒ श्नप्त्रे᳚स्थो॒ &lt;br>
विष्णो॒स्स्यूर॑सि॒ विष्णो᳚र्ध्रु॒वम॑सि वैष्ण॒वम॑सि॒ विष्ण॑वे त्वा ॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>तद॑स्य प्रि॒यम॒भिपाथो॑ अश्याम् । नरो॒ यत्र॑ देव॒यवो॒ मद॑न्ति । &lt;br>
उ॒रु॒क्र॒मस्य॒ स हि बन्धु॑रि॒त्था । विष्णोः᳚ प॒दे प॑र॒मे मध्व॒ उथ्सः॑ । &lt;br>
प्रतद्विष्णु॑स्स्तवते वी॒र्या॑य । मृ॒गो न भी॒मः कु॑च॒रो गि॑रि॒ष्ठाः । &lt;br>
यस्यो॒रुषु॑ त्रि॒षु वि॒क्रम॑णेषु । अधि॑क्षि॒यन्ति॒ भुव॑नानि॒ विश्वा᳚ । &lt;br>
प॒रो मात्र॑या त॒नुवा॑ वृधान । न ते॑ महि॒त्वमन्व॑श्नुवन्ति ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Narayan Suktam- नारायणसूक्तम्</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/narayan-suktam/</link><pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/narayan-suktam/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Vishnu.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">नारायणसूक्तम्
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%A3%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AE" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Narayan Suktam
&lt;div id="narayan-suktam" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#narayan-suktam" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
&lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/036-narayanSuktam.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>सहस्रशीर्षं देवं विश्वाक्षं विश्वशम्भुवम् । &lt;br>
विश्वं नारायणं देवं अक्षरं परमं पदम् ।&lt;/p>
&lt;p>विश्वतः परमान्नित्यं विश्वं नारायणग्ं हरिम् । &lt;br>
विश्वं एवेदं पुरुषस्तद्विश्वं उपजीवति ।&lt;/p>
&lt;p>पतिं विश्वस्यात्मेश्वरग्ं शाश्वतग्ं शिवमच्युतम् । &lt;br>
नारायणं महाज्ञेयं विश्वात्मानं परायणम् ।&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Mantrapushpam - मन्त्रपुष्पं</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/mantra-pushpam/</link><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/mantra-pushpam/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Vishnu.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">मन्त्रपुष्पं
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AA" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%AA" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 class="relative group">Mantra Pushpam
&lt;div id="mantra-pushpam" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#mantra-pushpam" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>ॐ यो॑ऽपां पुष्पं॒ वेद॑।  पुष्प॑वान् प्र॒जावा᳚न् पशु॒मान् भ॑वति ।&lt;br>
च॒न्द्रमा॒ वा अ॒पां पुष्पम्᳚।  पुष्प॑वान् प्र॒जावा᳚न् पशु॒मान् भ॑वति ।&lt;br>
य ए॒वं वेद॑ । यो॑ऽपामा॒यत॑नं॒ वेद॑ । आ॒यत॑नवान् भवति ॥ १॥&lt;/p>
&lt;p>अ॒ग्निर्वा अ॒पामा॒यत॑नम्।  आ॒यत॑नवान् भवति ।&lt;br>
